## ðŸ”„ How It Works

1. User enters feature values on Buy page
2. Click "Predict Price" button
3. Frontend validates and converts values to numbers
4. POST request sent to `http://localhost:5000/predict_api`
5. Backend processes with CatBoost model
6. Returns prediction value (in thousands)
7. Frontend displays as formatted price

